<p><strong>Experiment Number</strong> : 5018-C</p>
<div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div>
<p><strong>Protocol:</strong> SCP-5018 runs on a standard computer terminal connected to a motorized lock.</p>
<div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div>
<p><strong>Results:</strong> SCP-5018 was unable to access the mechanism. It then proceeded to replicate as observed in Experiment 5018-A. Computer terminal was powered off.</p>
