<div class="colmod-content">
<blockquote>
<p><tt>Alright, so I found something else. This time hiding in the source code of Experiment 5018-B. Has something to do with the font size of some of the letters. There aren't numbers or anything, so I think the order from top to bottom should be correct. What is happening? I don't get what's going on. It's frustrating. I guess I'll keep looking.</tt></p>
